            </td>
            


<td class="answercell">
    <div class="post-text" itemprop="text">
<p>I was successfully able to solve (in my case for fonts) using htaccess but obviously, OP is asking little different. But you can use FileMatch pattern and add any sort of extension so that it won't give cros error.</p>

<pre><code>&lt;IfModule mod_headers.c&gt;
  &lt;FilesMatch "\.(ttf|ttc|otf|eot|woff|woff2|font.css|css)$"&gt;
    Header set Access-Control-Allow-Origin "*"
  &lt;/FilesMatch&gt;
&lt;/IfModule&gt;
</code></pre>

<p><a href="https://httpd.apache.org/docs/2.4/mod/core.html#filesmatch" rel="nofollow noreferrer">https://httpd.apache.org/docs/2.4/mod/core.html#filesmatch</a></p>
    </div>
    <table class="fw">
    <tr>
