<td class="answercell">
    <div class="post-text" itemprop="text">
<p>Just to mention another way of "bypassing" it - AJAX proxy. Send request to your server to fetch the data from another origin and send the request back to you.</p>

<p>I prefer this approach over JSONP because it has some potential security issues.</p>
    </div>
