<td class="answercell">
    <div class="post-text" itemprop="text">
<p>Perhaps you can copy the resource from the Production server to the Development 
server, and have the url to the resource to adjust dynamically. In that way you would be reading always from the same origin, eliminating the cross origin exception. </p>
